        "evidence": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The WAST Score is calculated by the addition of the selected points:</span></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"width: 100%; height: 1434px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 51.365187713310576%;\"><col style=\"width: 28.668941979522184%;\"><col style=\"width: 19.795221843003414%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Variable</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\"></td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Points</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>WAST-Short</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>In general, how would you describe your relationship?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No tension</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Some tension</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>A lot of tension</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Do you and your partner work out arguments with:</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>No difficulty</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Some difficulty</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Great difficulty</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td colspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Additional Questions</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 138px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Do arguments ever result in you feeling down or bad about yourself?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Never</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sometimes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 30px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 30px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Often</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 30px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Do arguments ever result in hitting, kicking, or pushing?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Never</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sometimes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Often</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Do you ever feel frightened by what your partner says or does?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Never</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sometimes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Often</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner ever abused you physically?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Never</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sometimes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Often</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner ever abused you emotionally?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Never</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>1</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Sometimes</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>2</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Often</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>3</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 54px;\">\n<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"height: 162px;\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Has your partner ever abused you sexually?</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 54px;