        "facts": "<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>The additional questions are only shown if the first two questions are given a score of 3.</span></p>\n<p><b>&nbsp;</b></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Interpretation:</span><b></b></p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" align=\"left\">\n<table style=\"width: 58.87372013651876%;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 48.66666666666667%;\"><col style=\"width: 51%;\"></colgroup>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>WAST Score</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Screening Result</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>&lt;13</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Negative</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>&ge;13</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><span>Positive</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p></p>",
